## 6. Responsive Behavior

| Breakpoint | Behavior |
|------------|----------|
| **Desktop (> 768px)** | Full card with horizontal DescriptionList, all info visible |
| **Tablet (576-768px)** | DescriptionList stacks vertically, commit message truncated |
| **Mobile (< 576px)** | Compact mode auto-enabled, minimal info, tap to expand |

### Implementation Strategy

```typescript
// Use PatternFly responsive props
<DescriptionList
  isHorizontal={{ 
    default: false,  // Mobile: vertical
    md: true         // Tablet+: horizontal
  }}
  columnModifier={{ 
    default: '1Col', 
    lg: '2Col' 
  }}
/>

// Conditional truncation
const truncatedMessage = useBreakpoint({
  default: message.slice(0, 30) + '...',
  md: message.slice(0, 50) + '...',
  lg: message,
});
```

