## 8. Accessibility

| Requirement | Implementation |
|-------------|----------------|
| **Progress bar** | `aria-label="Feature completion progress"`, `aria-valuenow`, `aria-valuemin`, `aria-valuemax` |
| **Refresh button** | `aria-label="Refresh progress data"`, Tooltip for sighted users |
| **Commit tooltip** | Keyboard accessible via `Tooltip` tabIndex |
